description:
On today’s show, Emily is answering emails and giving insight to your sex and relationship quandaries.

She covers which foods can make or break your sex drive, how to know if your partner is bad for YOU – or just bad at relationships, and what to do when your partner is “too” close with an ex. Plus, she gives some tips on how to get past your partner’s self-love habits.
